OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fa few showers. Becoming dry this
OL,7,Fafternoon with any showers dying out,
OL,8,Falong with some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers dying out this
OL,12,Fevening. Then dry with clear spells,
OL,13,Fturning rather chilly in places.
OL,14,FThickening cloud will bring rain later
OL,15,Fin the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,18,Frain for a time. Dry and somewhat
OL,19,Fbrighter in the afternoon. Further
OL,20,Frain spreading north in the evening.
OL,21,FWarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
