OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright and warm on Friday, chance of
OL,7,Fsome rain on Friday night. Then dry
OL,8,Fand warm over the weekend with some
OL,9,Fbrightness.
